1152
00:53:43,180 --> 00:53:44,900
 ona meni zaustavi

1153
00:53:44,900 --> 00:53:45,120
 i kaže,

1154
00:53:45,120 --> 00:53:46,200
 Daniel, Daniel, Daniel,

1155
00:53:46,200 --> 00:53:46,400
 ej,

1156
00:53:46,400 --> 00:53:48,400
 daj me se slušaj,

1157
00:53:48,400 --> 00:53:49,480
