1295
00:57:19,200 --> 00:57:20,680
 ako mi nije s tobom ono,

1296
00:57:20,680 --> 00:57:21,100
 ok,

1297
00:57:21,100 --> 00:57:21,420
 onda,

1298
00:57:21,420 --> 00:57:22,740
 ono,

